{"tid":118750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年青工程師於超市女職員身後自瀆 CCTV黃雀在後","createTime":"2017-02-13T08:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T05:22:56.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f338a68c2ff69d7f87ca65e7a564ab956249a2","tid":118750,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:42:44.000Z","msg":"26歲的年青工程師於上周二(7日)，於旺角上海街的惠康超市內，於一名女職員身後露械並自瀆，結果被女職員發現，全程亦被超市的閉路電視拍下。工程師羅靖德今在裁判法院承認一項作出有違公德的行為罪，裁判官將押後至2月27日判刑，期間被告須還柙等候其背景及社會服務令報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170213/56298694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170213%2F56298694&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=338b5768\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170213%2F56298694&h=54373c70\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170213/56298694</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9fd6cf4c470885dfac799c387c809bc06ad19c","tid":118750,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"312af1dd21a83b9bea65e27338a8c6ba81d724af","tid":118750,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪中大engine?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能測試緊時間停頓掣"},{"pid":"349d8fb3a5e2881a049db1f0d1b6101875ac6dcb","tid":118750,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f617a0d6026c071efc864c2663890e293860e2a","tid":118750,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"測試失敗，時間停止原來唔work"},{"pid":"da9dd668278f6da24b267cf4688881f2a06262db","tid":118750,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit